===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|knelen|lang=enm}}, {{term|knewlen|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|cnēowlian||to kneel}}, equivalent to {{suffix|knee|le}}. Cognate with {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|knielen||to kneel|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|nds|-}} {{term|knelen||to kneel|lang=nds}}, {{etyl|de|-}} dialectal {{term|knielen|lang=de}}, {{term|kneulen|lang=de}}, {{term|knülen||to kneel|lang=de}}, {{etyl|da|-}} {{term|knæle||to kneel|lang=da}}.

